me, which I found fascinating,

00:16:46.757 --> 00:16:51.272
but the more I hear your
story, I'm connecting dots.

00:16:51.272 --> 00:16:53.365
You aren't just known for writing

00:16:53.365 --> 00:16:54.450
and directing these great films.

00:16:54.450 --> 00:16:56.007
There's also a famous character

00:16:56.007 --> 00:16:59.189
in popular fiction that
is based off of you.

00:16:59.189 --> 00:17:00.595
