00:17:13.148 --> 00:17:15.364
so he created, you can look it up.

00:17:15.364 --> 00:17:17.341
Say Francis Coppola Han Solo

00:17:17.341 --> 00:17:19.055
(audience laughs)
and you'll, you'll find that.

00:17:19.055 --> 00:17:21.323
So I'm sort of a dashing failure.

00:17:21.323 --> 00:17:24.339
(audience laughs)

00:17:24.339 --> 00:17:26.640
- How do you, do you agree with that?

