But in life, learning
is as much a pleasure

00:19:33.375 --> 00:19:36.230
as any of those things
and there's no bad part.

00:19:36.230 --> 00:19:39.032
There's no, it doesn't bite you back.

00:19:39.032 --> 00:19:40.973
You can't learn too much and overload.

00:19:40.973 --> 00:19:43.258
Oh, I've over learned this
month, I just don't feel well.

00:19:43.258 --> 00:19:45.243
