No one ever told me at the
beginning of my education

00:20:32.179 --> 00:20:34.640
what a lot of joyous fun it was.

00:20:34.640 --> 00:20:37.213
It always had me scared that I was gonna

00:20:37.213 --> 00:20:39.896
get that visit from Miss
Henchman to my father

00:20:39.896 --> 00:20:42.038
and then I would get a, you know.

00:20:42.038 --> 00:20:44.107
In those days, there was you got hit

00:20:44.107 --> 00:20:48.263
if you got bad report cards, which I did,

00:20:48.263 --> 00:20:52.434
